biography: Courtney Act is the drag persona of Shane Gilberto Jenek, an Australian drag queen, pop singer, entertainer and reality television personality.
RuPaul Andre Charles is an American drag queen, television judge, musician, and model. RuPaul has produced, hosted, and judged the reality competition series RuPaul's Drag Race since 2009.
